      {
        "id": "3bd3672d-baac-45e4-94ea-fac1c1e22e1e",
        "purpose": "describing",
        "value": "One important thing to note if you are considering installing a WhisperRoom: it will require a call to Facilities and the Fire Marshall, who will need to cut holes for fire suppression. Make sure to include this in your budget!",
